doc.after: Most of the visitors attracted to Jakarta are domestic tourists from all over Indonesia As the gateway of Indonesia Jakarta often serves as the stop over for foreign visitors on their way to Indonesian popular tourist destinations such as Bali and Yogyakarta Other than attracted to monuments landmarks and museums around Merdeka square and Jakarta Old Town tourist attractions include Taman Mini Indonesia Indah Ragunan Zoo Sunda Kelapa old port and the Ancol Dreamland complex on Jakarta Bay including Dunia Fantasi theme park Sea World Atlantis Water Adventure and Gelanggang Samudra
